text: Wilhelm Brenna (born 8 October 1979) is a retired Norwegian ski jumper. In the World Cup he finished once among the top 15, with a thirteenth place from Kuopio in March 1997. He became world junior champion in the normal hill the same year. He finished third overall in the Continental Cup in the 1998/99 season. ==References== * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male ski jumpers Category:People from Hedmark
